fields.content: Your mother was a hamster, and your father smells of elderberries!
You empty-headed animal food trough wiper!
I fart in your general direction!
Go away or I shall taunt you a second time!
Why do you think I have this outrageous accent, you silly king?
You don't frighten us with your silly knees-bent running around advancing behavior!
I wave my private parts at your aunties, you cheesy lot of second hand electric donkey bottom biters!
I wave my private parts at your aunties, you cheesy lot of second hand electric donkey bottom biters!
You don't frighten us, English pig dogs!
Go and boil your bottoms, you sons of a silly person!
I blow my nose at you, so-called 'Arthur King', you and all your silly English K-nig-hts.
